!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta(content="text/html" charset="UTF-8" http-equiv='Content-Type')
  %body
    %h1 Welcome to Ladder Manager!
    %h2 You've been made an admin of #{@user.organization.name}
    %p
      To login, simply go to 
      %a(href="http://laddermanager.com#{new_user_session_path}" title="Ladder Manager Sign In") http://laddermanager.com#{new_user_session_path}
      and login with the following credentials:
    %p
      Email: #{@user.email}
      %br
      Password: #{@password}
    %p
      We highly recommend visiting the "My Account" page after your first sign in and changing your password.
    %p
      %br
      Matt - Developer of
      %a(href="http://www.laddermanager.com" title="Ladder Manager") LadderManager.com
